import Mathlib

open Complex Set
open scoped Topology

/-- If f : U ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ is a holomorphic function on an open set U ‚äÜ ‚ÑÇ, then f is analytic on U.

In Lean: for an open set U : Set ‚ÑÇ and f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ, if f is complex-differentiable on U
(DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f U), then AnalyticOn ‚ÑÇ f U. -/
theorem analyticOn_of_differentiableOn {U : Set ‚ÑÇ} {f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ} (h : DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f U) :
  AnalyticOn ‚ÑÇ f U := by sorry
